text: Xu Yinghui (born 7 January 1989) is a Chinese cross-country skier. She competed in the women's 15 kilometre pursuit at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of China Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Chinese female biathletes Category:Asian Games medalists in biathlon Category:Biathletes at the 2011 Asian Winter Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for China Category:Medalists at the 2011 Asian Winter Games
